Priceless;;75;;82;;PG-13;;Irène (Audrey Tautou) loves nice things and loves to have wealthy men pay for them. One night, she mistakes Jean (Gad Elmaleh), a poor bartender, for a potential client and spends the night with him. The next morning, Irène realizes her mistake and leaves, but poor Jean is smitten with her. Later, when a rich dowager mistakes Jean for a veteran gigolo, Irène agrees to tutor him in the art of fleecing wealthy lovers.;;Romance,Comedy;;Pierre Salvadori;;2006;;Audrey Tautou,Gad Elmaleh,Marie-Christine Adam,Vernon Dobtcheff,Jacques Spiesser,Annelise Hesme,Didier Brice,Charlotte Vermeil;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/priceless